    <refsection id="Description_END_c">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            When it is activated by the input event, this block resets the end of the simulation
            to the specified time shorter than the value defined in the Simulation => Setup
            'final integration time' (scs_m.props.tf).
        </para>
        <para>
            Note that specifying a value greater than the 'Final simulation time' does NOT
            extend this one. This has no effect.
        </para>
    </refsection>

    <refsection id="Dialogbox_END_c">
        <title>Parameters</title>
        <inlinemediaobject>
            <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../../../../images/gui/END_c_gui.gif" align="center" style="float:right"/>
                    <!-- align => Javahelp, style => Online -->
            </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">Shortened simulation duration</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para>That parameter is a date for an initial output event. By using a
                    feed back from the event output port to the event input port, then
                    that block can end the simulation at the time defined by this
                    parameter.
                </para>
                <para>Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
        <para/>
